new trailer has been released for Matthew McConaughey&#8217;s &#8220;GOLD&#8221; ahead of its release later this month.Based on a true story, &#8220;GOLD&#8221; follows Kenny Wells (McConaughey), a prospector desperate for a lucky break as he attempts to discover gold in the uncharted jungle of Indonesia.He manages to return a rich man, however although getting the gold was hard, it may be even harder to keep it, as Wells soon finds out.Directed by &#8220;Syriana&#8221; helmer Stephen Gaghan, the film also stars Edgar Ramirez and Bryce Dallas Howard.&#8220;GOLD&#8221; hits theaters January 27.-Relaxnews